Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 ${shlibs:Depends},
Description: LXQt system integration plugin for Qt
 With this plugin, all Qt-based programs can adopt settings of
 LXQt, such as the icon theme.
 .
 This package provides the lxqt qtplugin interface. 

